{"tid":1519734,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"各位和理非，831一定要出黎","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:33:43.000Z","uid":30246,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4837c0a990f16f0309f7d44155355da9c8ee59","tid":1519734,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"其實共產黨已經冇招可以出<br />\n出老解又明顯地破壞一國兩際，結果憲制上攬炒<br />\n緊急法又驚外資走晒，結果經濟上攬炒<br />\n所以林奠首先<span style=\"color: red;\">唔批831遊行</span><br />\n又派黑社會<span style=\"color: red;\">斬傷遊行發起人</span><br />\n前一日830不停<span style=\"color: red;\">拘捕知名人士</span><br />\n再係狗記者會上<span style=\"color: red;\">散播做咩都可以拉你</span><br />\n目的只有一個<br />\n就係制造<span style=\"color: red;\">白色恐怖</span><br />\n等和理非唔敢出黎遊行<br />\n場運動佔多數既群體就係和理非<br />\n如果冇左和理非出黎backup<br />\n政府就可以利用黑警圍捕少數既勇武<br />\n圍捕後再對勇武控以暴動罪<br />\n<br />\n因為共產黨除左制造白色恐怖<br />\n真係無辦法可以阻止依場運動<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家聽日831各位和理非一定要出黎<br />\n除左捍衛香港人既自由<br />\n仲要保護為左香港將自己生命前途拎出黎作賭注既勇武<br />\n話比共產黨知我地香港人唔怕你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9aee924fb8600d280a39bc7acb8eea331b53a9b1","tid":1519734,"uid":278391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"我應承你明天見"},{"pid":"e92af4d90af680ea8ff7997dc2e12903bdfb9e0b","tid":1519734,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e23ce8673ded990267a1f8d69caf341e23146fba","tid":1519734,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"598b5dd6c6e5d6434e07c582b8c331201dabfd72","tid":1519734,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"8c7bfd973df2625789a77fa53072eb505206d624","tid":1519734,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"a2221db